These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, purple, lavender, orange
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person who likes orange is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | orange | azure     | lavender | purple |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, fisherman, analyst, manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the fisherman is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the manager is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the analyst is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Job   | accountant | fisherman    | manager     | analyst  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

