.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, lettuce, nectarine, avocado
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
2. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Food   | lettuce   | nectarine   | watermelon  | avocado |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, october, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Birthday   | may  | july   | february  | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue, azure, ivory
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who likes ivory is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Color      | light-blue | coral | azure       | ivory |

