.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, cat, bird
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the bird and the person drinking juice##2
3. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the cat and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Pet   | goldfish | frog  | cat    | bird  |

