.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, indian, thai
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, apricot, ivory, white
1. the person who likes white is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the person who likes apricot is the person who likes apricot##1
6. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes ivory and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| Color     | fuchsia | white  | apricot   | ivory |

