.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking, fishing
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, backgammon, scrabble
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing domino##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | filmmaking | board-games | drawing   |
| Game   | domino | backgammon | bridge      | scrabble |

