2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Transport     | van | ship   | helicopter      | motorbike      |
| Sport   | skiing     | tennis | basketball | volleyball |

