2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
6. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | filmmaking | writing    | chess      |
| Game   | bridge       | canasta       | go | mah-jongg |

