.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, lacrosse, sailing
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | tennis | lacrosse  | sailing | biathlon |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

