3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage  | artichoke | potato  | plum      |
| Transport    | scooter | tram | van | helicopter |

