.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, skateboarding, cricket
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, metal, techno
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
6. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | cricket | skateboarding | swimming |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | dubstep       | indie   | metal      |

