.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, rabbit, turtle, lizard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, indie, punk
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Pet      | rat | rabbit    | lizard  | turtle |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep | indie | punk  |

