3. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the fan of country and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Music-Genre   | indie | techno  | ambient  | country |
| Pet           | cat    | hamster | guinea-pig | dog |

