.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, trance, house, country
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard
1. the fan of country is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
2. the security-guard is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the doctor is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the fan of house##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | country        | metal       | house   | trance |
| Job    | security-guard | entrepreneur | doctor | coach  |

